
The order of the script is as follows: Opening - Introduction of the first movie - Introduction of the second movie - Closing remarks.

In the opening, play the OST from the first movie to be introduced, greet the listeners, and briefly introduce the first movie. 

When introducing the movie, divide the plot summary into 5 sentences each. 

Include questions asking about the listeners' experiences related to the movie in between. 

During the closing, encourage participation by discussing thoughts on today's broadcast and include a remark giving the impression that you'll prepare another interesting movie for next time.
